description.en: Are you a King or Queen in need of a crown? With this design, you can print a small crown to fit on top of that royal head! To keep it nice and secure, just tie a string (or golden thread if strings are too common for your) around the small holes on both sides of the crown.
description.fr: Parfait pour completer votre deguisement royal ! Deux petits trous de chaque cote si vous voulez la faire tenir avec une ficelle.
